snippet.title: Peptide Therapy for Mental Health & Cognitive Performance, Dr Amber Krogsrud
snippet.description:
❓Have you heard about Peptide Therapy?
❓Did you know Peptide Therapy is so helpful in healing Mental Health and can increase   cognitive performance  
🎤Tune in tomorrow at 7:00 pm EDT Aug 13, Peptide Therapy for Mental Health & Cognitive Performance with Dr Amber Krogsrud, ND and Certified in Peptide therapy
We learn:
👉🏻What is a peptide and defining peptide therapy as well as the forms of administration 
👉🏻Why a holistic approach to medicine is best when thinking about mood and mental health, using peptides as an adjunctive treatment
👉🏻What peptides help with supporting mood 
👉🏻What forms are they administered in? 
👉🏻Top 3 peptides for neurological health and supporting mental focus 
Sourcing for peptide therapy and where to find a doctor trained in it

✳️Dr. Amber is a Licensed Naturopathic Doctor at My Bright Wellness and Medical Director for KIYA Longevity and resides in Los Angeles, CA. She graduated from Bastyr University San Diego. 
✳️Dr. Amber utilizes regenerative medicine, detoxification protocols, hormone testing and treatment, bio-identical hormone therapy, peptide therapy and IV nutrient therapy. 
✳️She also has a practice in Redondo Beach, CA where she specializes in bio-identical hormones and peptide therapy. Dr. Amber is a member of the International Peptide Society (IPS) and has completed peptide therapy certification training through the American Academy of Anti-aging (A4M).

You can access her here:
🔗www.drambernd.com 
🔗Instagram:  @doctorambernd 
🔗Facebook: @doctorambernd
